OL,3,C'World first': Surgeon removes apple
OL,4,Csized brain tumours through eyebrows
OL,6,FA Scottish surgeon has found a way to
OL,7,Fremove brain tumours the size of
OL,8,Fapples through patients' eyebrows, in
OL,9,Fwhat is believed to be a world-first.
OL,11,FConsultant neurosurgeon Anastasios
OL,12,FGiamouriadis of NHS Grampian, has
OL,13,Fadapted an existing technique of
OL,14,Fkeyhole surgery to remove much larger
OL,15,Ftumours from the front of the brain
OL,16,Fthan was previously the case.
