OL,3,C'World first': Surgeon removes apple
OL,4,Csized brain tumours through eyebrows
OL,6,FThe new method takes far less time to
OL,7,Fcomplete than a conventional
OL,8,Fcraniotomy, which involves removing a
OL,9,Flarge part of the skull and can take
OL,10,Fup to eight hours to complete.
OL,12,FMr Giamouriadis said his keyhole
OL,13,Fmethod takes half that time and some
OL,14,Fpatients are even able to leave the
OL,15,Fhospital the next day.
