OL,3,C'World first': Surgeon removes apple
OL,4,Csized brain tumours through eyebrows
OL,6,F"I have modified and developed the
OL,7,Ftechnique with my team and we are
OL,8,Foperating on very large brain tumours
OL,9,Fin the front of the brain and as far
OL,10,Fback as the middle of the brain," he
OL,11,Fexplained.
OL,13,F"By doing this through the keyhole
OL,14,Fapproach through the eyebrow, it is
OL,15,Fmore challenging technically, but it
OL,16,Ftakes probably half the time ` if not
OL,17,Fless.
OL,19,F"The patient will go home the second
OL,20,Fday and be back to normal life in most
OL,21,Foccasions within a week or two.
