OL,3,C'World first': Surgeon removes apple
OL,4,Csized brain tumours through eyebrows
OL,6,F"We are not aware of anywhere else in
OL,7,Fthe world that has managed to remove
OL,8,Ftumours as large as we have."
OL,10,FDoreen Adams, 75, from Rosemount,
OL,11,FAberdeen, underwent the new procedure
OL,12,Flast year after she became ill from
OL,13,Fheadaches and had an unsuccessful
OL,14,Fcraniotomy while abroad.
OL,16,FShe said she felt "wonderful" after Mr
OL,17,FGiamouriadis' procedure and suffered
OL,18,Fonly a "black eye".
