OL,3,C'World first': Surgeon removes apple
OL,4,Csized brain tumours through eyebrows
OL,6,F"I felt great after the operation,"
OL,7,Fshe said. "I was left with a black eye
OL,8,Fand it took a while for it to open,
OL,9,Fbut that was all."
OL,11,FMr Giamouradis and his team have
OL,12,Fperformed the new procedure on 48
OL,13,Fpatients so far.
OL,15,FHe added that he is working with the
OL,16,FUniversity of Aberdeen to teach other
OL,17,Fsurgeons how to perform the new
OL,18,Fprocedure using virtual reality.
